title: HIIT Workout - Insane 15 Minute Spin Bike Workout
description:
Try this insane 15 minute spin bike workout today! 

You don't have to spend countless hours busting your butt and sweating buckets to obtain benefits like weight loss, muscle growth, and improved overall health and well-being.

15 Minute Spin Bike HIIT workouts like this one save you time without sacrificing any fitness benefits!
